    X = [x0] + X
    Y = [y0]
    n = len(X)
    for k in range(1, n):

        m1 = df(X[k-1], Y[k-1])
        m2 = df(X[k-1] + (3/4)*h, Y[k-1] + (3/4)*h*m1)
        yk = Y[k-1] + (h/3)*(m1 + 2*m2)
